    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Schistura scyphovecteta, n. sp.: a. holotype, MUMF 11136, 39.4 mm SL, female (lateral view); b. holotype (dorsal view); c. holotype (ventral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5268952/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5268950>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Mizoram: stream Kolchaw at Kolchaw, collection site of Schistura nebeshwari; looking upstreams and to the east. Photo: Y. Lokeshwor." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5268950/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5268954>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Oromandibular structures of Schistura scyphovecteta (MUMF 11140, 31.4 mm SL). A. Ventral surface of head. B. Magnified portion of ventral surface of head. C. Close up box i in A, showing taste bud on rostral barbel. D. Close up box ii in B, showing unculi on lower jaw. E. Close up box iii in B, showing skin fold on upper lip. F. Close up box iv in B, showing taste bud on lower lip. LJ ─ lower jaw; LL ─ lower lip; RB ─ rostral barbel; UL ─ upper lip; TB ─ taste bud; SF ─ skin fold." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5268954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5268956>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Lip structure of Schistura scyphovecteta (MUMF 11136, 39.4 mm SL). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5268956/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5268960>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Schistura scyphovecteta (MUMF 11139, 37.8 mm SL) showing a. free posterior chambers of air bladders; b. coiling patterns of intestine. pab — posterior chamber of air bladder. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5268960/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5268946>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Map showing type locality of Schistura nebeshwari and Schistura scyphovecteta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5268946/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5268962>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Mizoram: stream Ka-ao near New Serkawr, collection site of Schistura scyphovecteta; looking upstreams and to the southeast. Photo: Y. Lokeshwor." ;
